  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "You are a lonely satanist trying to summon a demon date.\n\nRead pages
    from the Necronomicon to build Power. More Power means stronger demons, better
    rewards, and more danger.\n\nEach page may give you:\n\nPower \u2014 determines
    which demon you summon.\nRizz \u2014 improves your chance to win a date.\nTape
    \u2014 lets you repair new pages and add them to your book.\nSanity Loss \u2014
    pushes you closer to the end of your run.\n\nDuring a summoning, choose:\n\nKeep
    Reading\nGain more Power and rewards, but risk going too far.\n\nStop Reading\nLock
    in your Power and summon a demon.\n\nWatch the Dagger pages. If you read too
    many dangerous pages in one summoning, you summon Papiyawn and lose.\n\nAlso
    watch your Sanity. If it reaches 0, something else may come looking for love.\n\nAfter
    you summon a demon, choose:\n\nDate\nRoll a D20 against your Rizz. If the roll
    is equal to or lower than your Rizz, you win that demon\u2019s date ending.\n\nGive
    Up\nAvoid the date roll and take the demon\u2019s Boon and Bane.\n\nBoons and
    Banes can help or hurt future summonings.\n\nBetween summonings, spend Tape in
    the shop to repair torn pages. Repaired pages are added to the Necronomicon and
    can appear in later readings.\n\nRepair more pages, build a better book, keep
    your Sanity, and try to find love before the Necronomicon ruins your life."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 66af7cbdd9e525b428b4fd1f7b769842, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 7198656019263021574, guid: 66af7cbdd9e525b428b4fd1f7b769842, type: 2}
